title: Arkanium (01 - 05)(2002 - 2003)(Wildcard+Shinter-OCD)
description:
Arkanium (01 - 05)(2002 - 2003)(Wildcard+Shinter-OCD)


Arkanium revolves around the search for a collection of mystically powered scrolls. Their legend suggests that whomever unlocks its secrets will attain psychic and physical perfection, becoming something like a god on Earth. Rowan an American weapons designer and part-time mercenary and Shing, a proud spiritual statesman who works within a newly formed government of China. find themselves linked and fighting common enemies
